data.description: Seller is offering a $5000 concession to buy down the rate which will help with the land lease!!!   Welcome to one of the nicest floor plans/homes in the community! This is a 3 bedroom/2-bathroom, 1433 square foot home with tons of upgrades. The first thing you notice when you step into the home is the luxury vinyl flooring that runs throughout the home. The beautiful kitchen has ample storage with tons of cabinets and plenty of room to gather round the kitchen island. There is also a dining room to enjoy your evening get togethers! There is a cool pot filler as well. The laundry room has plenty of space plus built ins to make your folding life easier. The living room is very cozy and includes a stone surrounded electric fireplace with a big sliding glass door that goes out to your concrete patio and fenced yard. The primary bedroom has its own ensuite with a double sink, large walk-in shower and a walk-in closet. There are two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. There is an oversized 2 car garage that has access to the backyard. The home is located on a four-foot crawlspace that can be used for extra storage.
